title: They Never Saw it Coming
author: VD
content_html: Remember, the SJWs at YouTube are convinced they are not only your moral, but your intellectual superiors. But in fairness to them, it’s not as if anyone could have possibly seen this very difficult and technologically accomplished hack coming.
